Class BalloonsBlocks

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.leonic.balloons.init.BalloonsBlocks

  • public class BalloonsBlocks
extends java.lang.Object
    A class which calls the RegisterHelper to register the blocks on startup. For custom model blocks we don't use RegisterHelper.

    0.2
    Author:
